# Ω_BLACKSTAR – Tool List with Descriptions

1. Nmap           - Network scanning and reconnaissance
2. Git            - Version control system
3. Termux API     - Access device features (camera, GPS, etc.)
4. Metasploit     - Penetration testing framework
5. Hydra          - Password cracking tool
6. SQLmap         - SQL injection testing
7. Recon-ng       - OSINT framework
8. theHarvester   - Email and domain harvesting
9. SocialFish     - Phishing tool (social media)
10. HiddenEye     - Advanced phishing toolkit
11. Ngrok         - Secure tunnels to localhost
12. Cloudflared   - Cloudflare tunnel (for exposing local servers)
13. IP-Tracer     - Track IP addresses
14. WHOIS         - Domain registration lookup
15. OpenSSL       - SSL/TLS toolkit
16. Curl          - HTTP requests and data transfer
17. Wget          - File downloader
18. Python        - Programming language
19. Pip           - Python package manager
20. Nmap Full     - All nmap scripts and features
